  <h1 class="gd-h1">Canada vs Alaska Heliskiing</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">The short answer: choose Canada for reliable powder, forgiving terrain and the best odds of skiing every day; choose Alaska if you are an expert chasing the steepest lines on earth. Below we compare them honestly and give you a clear framework — see our <a href="/packages">packages</a> and our third path in <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
